#. Max bytes: 52
msgctxt "Offset_0x232B0_Len_52"
msgid "Ah, come to think of it, Gen-san hasn't sung lately."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 51
msgctxt "Offset_0x235A0_Len_51"
msgid "But don't y'enjoy listenin' to other folks singing?"
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 55
msgctxt "Offset_0x23810_Len_55"
msgid "Sure, I like listening 'bout as much as I like singin'."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 53
msgctxt "Offset_0x23850_Len_53"
msgid "因為我喜歡唱卡拉OK，也喜歡聽別人唱啊"
